(256, 1, '2013-09-14 18:20:16', '2013-09-15 01:20:16', 'The staff at Tamriel Foundry value your feedback! If you have any comments, questions, or concerns about the website we would love to hear them. Please use this form to send us a note and we''ll respond to you as soon as possible.\r\n<div class="instructions">\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Please do not use this contact form to ask simple questions about <em>The Elder Scrolls Online</em> without first reading the <a title="Read the Development FAQ" href="http://tamrielfoundry.com/development-faq/" target="_blank">Development FAQ</a>.</li>\r\n	<li>This form is intended for website related inquiries, not as a Q&amp;A about <em>ESO</em>.</li>\r\n	<li>Contact form submissions are handled by Tamriel Foundry''s volunteer staff, but we will do our best to respond to all contacts within 48 hours!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>', 'Contact Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'contact-us', '', '', '2013-09-14 18:33:08', '2013-09-15 01:33:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/?page_id=256', 0, 'page', '', 0),
