(261, 1, '2013-09-16 12:25:24', '2013-09-16 19:25:24', 'Praesent justo sem, venenatis non nulla ac, malesuada cursus elit. Pellentesque consequat placerat augue in condimentum. Curabitur quis felis sit amet leo condimentum viverra vitae sed tortor. Proin volutpat risus ut sollicitudin hendrerit. Donec porta felis id ipsum tincidunt, ac laoreet ante suscipit. Quisque pulvinar massa a faucibus hendrerit. Vestibulum mollis egestas venenatis. Morbi et est mauris. Sed vel euismod neque. Vestibulum vehicula justo tincidunt, ullamcorper nisi et, hendrerit tortor. Curabitur posuere lectus ac nunc lobortis volutpat. Nam vehicula, tellus ut facilisis sagittis, ipsum eros porta velit, a pretium turpis enim eu odio.\r\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/swamp.jpg"><img class="size-large wp-image-57 aligncenter" alt="swamp" src="http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/swamp-600x405.jpg" width="600" height="405" /></a></p>\r\nUt non mollis nisl. Aenean eget congue dolor. Ut diam urna, pharetra sit amet dapibus id, volutpat a lorem. Vivamus ac tincidunt lectus, quis accumsan massa. Suspendisse sagittis neque tellus, sed sodales mi ultricies sit amet. Vestibulum a sapien venenatis, semper sem tincidunt, vestibulum mauris. Ut viverra orci quis neque tempor, id eleifend mauris venenatis.\r\n<h2>Header 2</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Unordered list elements in main posts look like this.</li>\r\n	<li>Second item, with sub-items\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Nested list items</li>\r\n	<li>Nested list 2</li>\r\n	<li>Nested list 3</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>Third item</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAlternatively, ordered lists have the following appearance:\r\n<h3>Header 3</h3>\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style="line-height: 16px;">First entry</span></li>\r\n	<li>Second entry</li>\r\n	<li>Third entry, with sub entries\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Nested entry one</li>\r\n	<li>Nested entry 2</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<blockquote>I also frequently employ block quotes, which should have a unique appearance.\r\n<p style="text-align: right;">-somebody</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p style="text-align: left;">Here''s a bit more content after the quote.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n[caption id="attachment_51" align="aligncenter" width="450"]<a href="http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/glow-forest.jpg"><img class="size-medium wp-image-51 " alt="Let''s finish up with a caption" src="http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/glow-forest-450x190.jpg" width="450" height="190" /></a> Let''s finish up with a caption[/caption]', 'Tamriel Foundry Theme Updated', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '42-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-09-16 12:25:24', '2013-09-16 19:25:24', '', 42, 'http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/2013/09/42-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
